text: Malonakaryakovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Staroarzamatovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 454 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Mishkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Malonakaryakovo
